\n\ttext-indent:-.25in;}\n@list l0:level5\n\t{mso-level-tab-stop:2.5in;\n\tmso-level-number-position:left;\n\ttext-indent:-.25in;}\n@list l0:level6\n\t{mso-level-tab-stop:3.0in;\n\tmso-level-number-position:left;\n\ttext-indent:-.25in;}\n@list l0:level7\n\t{mso-level-tab-stop:3.5in;\n\tmso-level-number-position:left;\n\ttext-indent:-.25in;}\n@list l0:level8\n\t{mso-level-tab-stop:4.0in;\n\tmso-level-number-position:left;\n\ttext-indent:-.25in;}\n@list l0:level9\n\t{mso-level-tab-stop:4.5in;\n\tmso-level-number-position:left;\n\ttext-indent:-.25in;}\nol\n\t{margin-bottom:0in;}\nul\n\t{margin-bottom:0in;}\n-->\n</style>\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\n <o:shapedefaults v:ext=\"edit\" spidmax=\"1026\" />\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\n <o:shapelayout v:ext=\"edit\">\n  <o:idmap v:ext=\"edit\" data=\"1\" />\n </o:shapelayout></xml><![endif]-->\n</head>\n\n<body lang=EN-US link=blue vlink=purple>\n\n<div class=Section1>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='color:#1F497D'>FYI<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='color:#1F497D'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<div>\n\n<div style='border:none;border-top:solid #B5C4DF 1.0pt;padding:3.0pt 0in 0in 0in'>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><b><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Tahoma\",\"sans-serif\"'>From:</span></b><span\nstyle='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Tahoma\",\"sans-serif\"'> John Amerling\n[mailto:john_amerling@earthlink.net] <br>\n<b>Sent:</b> Wednesday, March 05, 2008 10:43 AM<br>\n<b>To:</b> Darren Indyke<br>\n<b>Subject:</b> <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal>I just pulled an article from the internet and it does a far\nbetter job than I could in summarizing the meeting. My short take on it was:<o:p></o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoListParagraph style='text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span\nstyle='mso-list:Ignore'>1.<span style='font:7.0pt \"Times New Roman\"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><![endif]>The applicant came into the meeting trying to emphasize\nthat the proposal was backed by local persons, as opposed to off island\ncontinentals, who ought to be supported.<o:p></o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoListParagraph style='text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span\nstyle='mso-list:Ignore'>2.<span style='font:7.0pt \"Times New Roman\"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><![endif]>The proposal, they said orally, was not to build and\noperate a replica of the Willy T as depicted in their written application;\ninstead the project was an ecologically driven effort to provide moorings to\nsave the ocean floor and educate children and the only way to pay to install\nand maintain them was to use revenues generated by the restaurant.<o:p></o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoListParagraph style='text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span\nstyle='mso-list:Ignore'>3.<span style='font:7.0pt \"Times New Roman\"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><![endif]>The audience and even the Commission seemed skeptical\nabout this politically correct spin.<o:p></o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoListParagraph style='text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span\nstyle='mso-list:Ignore'>4.<span style='font:7.0pt \"Times New Roman\"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><![endif]>Note that the snake oil salesman employed by the\napplicant was Marshall Bell. <o:p></o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoListParagraph style='text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span\nstyle='mso-list:Ignore'>5.<span style='font:7.0pt \"Times New Roman\"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><![endif]>The Commission has 30 days to make a decision.<o:p></o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoListParagraph><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal>I will send the article in a separate e mail. &nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal>Lafayette Contractors, LLC<o:p></o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal>6100 Red Hook Quarters, Suite A2-7<o:p></o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal>St. Thomas, VI 00802<i><o:p></o:p></i></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal>340 779-8054 (O)<o:p></o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal>340 779-8055 (FAX)<o:p></o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal>340 690-7194 (Cell)<o:p></o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n\n</div>\n\n</body>\n\n</html>\n","is_from_epstein":false,"attachments":0,"avatar_color":"#db4437","stars":9,"is_redacted":false}]